trans-unit.source: Provides data for preprocess input events.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för preprocess inkommande händelser.

trans-unit.source: Canceling a pre-process input stops the input from being processed further.
trans-unit.target: Avbryta en före processer inmatning stoppar indata från bearbetas ytterligare.

trans-unit.source: Listen for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput> to determine if another handler canceled a pre-process input.
trans-unit.target: Lyssna efter den <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput>att avgöra om en annan hanterare avbryta före behandla indata.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput>

trans-unit.source: The input staging area processes input into [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] events.
trans-unit.target: Inkommande mellanlagringsområdet bearbetar indata till [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] händelser.

trans-unit.source: All <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput> event handlers are called, even if one of the handlers cancels the input.
trans-unit.target: Alla <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput>händelsehanterare kallas även om en hanterare avbryter indata.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput>

trans-unit.source: To verify if a handler further up the tree canceled the input, listen for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput> event.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill kontrollera om en hanterare ytterligare uppåt i trädet avbryta indata lyssna efter den <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput>händelse.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput>

trans-unit.source: PreProcessInputEventArgs is used with the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput> event.
trans-unit.target: PreProcessInputEventArgs används med den <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput>händelse.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput>

trans-unit.source: Input is processed in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] in the follow stages: 1.
trans-unit.target: Indata har bearbetats i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] i följande steg: 1.

trans-unit.source: Pre-process stage.
trans-unit.target: Förbearbeta steget.

trans-unit.source: The input manager raises the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput> event.
trans-unit.target: Inkommande manager aktiverar den <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput>händelse.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreProcessInput>

trans-unit.source: Pre-notify stage.
trans-unit.target: Meddela före steget.

trans-unit.source: The input manager raises the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput> event.
trans-unit.target: Inkommande manager aktiverar den <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput>händelse.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PreNotifyInput>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] input event or events are raised.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] händelse eller händelser aktiveras.

trans-unit.source: Post-notify stage.
trans-unit.target: Meddela efter steget.

trans-unit.source: The input manager raises the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PostNotifyInput> event.
trans-unit.target: Inkommande manager aktiverar de <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PostNotifyInput>händelse.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PostNotifyInput>

trans-unit.source: Post-process stage.
trans-unit.target: Bearbeta efter steget.

trans-unit.source: The input manager raises the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PostProcessInput> event.
trans-unit.target: Inkommande manager aktiverar den <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PostProcessInput>händelse.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputManager.PostProcessInput>
